headline: Collage Group Releases 2025 State of Brand Cultural Fluency Report, with Procter & Gamble, Mars, Nestle, Sony, and Google Making the Top 20

The Top 20 Brands include Dawn, Vicks, Bounty, M&M’s, Nestle, Sony, and Google.
